<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9232] Can&apos;t Swap Cores in New Admin UI</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9232</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using the Core Admin page on the new Admin UI, there is no way to submit a Swap Cores request. After choosing the Swap action for an existing core and selecting a core to swap with, clicking the Swap Cores button does nothing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12981073">SOLR-9232</key>
            <summary>Can&apos;t Swap Cores in New Admin UI</summary>
