                            <comment id="15407061" author="arafalov" created="Thu, 4 Aug 2016 03:08:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed and tested for non-Cloud use. If the functionality not suitable for Cloud, perhaps we need a separate JIRA to hide the button when in cloud mode. But this one (regression) has been fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15418782" author="arafalov" created="Fri, 12 Aug 2016 12:58:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In the cloud mode, there is Cores screen and the Collections screen does not have Swap button. So, we only need to cover the standalone mode.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
